race.description: Feral Franky @ Stud Future Stars Ht 1 H
race.comment: TOMMY'S AVA (8) steps out for the first time at this track. Comes here a last start placegetter at Wagga in a Grade 5 (18.45). Winning claims. LITTLE KING (1) produced a moderate effort last time when fifth at this track over 400m behind Wonder I Do (23.37) in a Mix. Scored at his previous run. Has won four of five starts from this draw. Key runner on best form. KIANDO DIVA (4) was out of the placings last time when fifth at Gunnedah (25.44) but did record second best time of the card when winning three back. Should be thereabouts. MOTOR CITY CHIEF (7) placed last time and cannot be ignored.
